snippet.title: Pixy-Pic-Xel PV
snippet.description:
Create colorful images on grid-based logic puzzle game Pixy-Pic-Xel, reminiscent to games such as Nonograms, Griddlers and Picross. Over 100 standard puzzles + 400 abstract puzzles (More than 500 puzzles total!).  Coming soon to Android!

Like/Follow Aya Saaya on twitter for the latest updates: https://twitter.com/PureAyaSaaya


Music Used: Wingless Seraph music "LifePlace-Magic Shop" by YouFulca, site: https://wingless-seraph.net/
